text.tspan: Average daily per capita protein supply, measured in grams of total protein per day.
Data source: Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations (2024)
Note: Data measures the availability delivered to households but does not necessarily indicate the quantity of protein actually consumed
(food may be wasted at the consumer level).
